@DATABASE "ISplitnJoin"

@NODE MAIN "ISplitnJoin"

                            
                        IntuiSplit & Join V1.23
                       ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
               A little program that can split and join files...
                A little combination of IntuiSplit and IntuiJoin

                                   by
                             Fredrik Söderberg


                            @{" Introduction          " Link 0.}
                            @{" Disclaimer            " Link 1.}
                            @{" Requirements          " Link 2.}
                            @{" Installation          " Link 3.}
                            @{" Usage                 " Link 4.}
                            @{" Contacting the Author " Link 5.}
                            @{" History               " Link 6.}
                            @{" Bugs                  " Link 7.}

@ENDNODE

@NODE 0. "Introduction"
Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~
What does this little program do ?
Well, its just a little combination of IntuiSplit and IntuiJoin.
It can split and join files.
I wrote this as an addition to my former split & join programs.

@ENDNODE

@NODE 1. "Disclaimer"
